    "We experimented with both Qwen2-Audio-7B and Qwen2-Audio-7B-Instruct for English-to-German speech translation.",
    "As Table 4 the \"Instruct\" model outperforms its base version.",
    "Hence, we use Qwen2-Audio-7B-Instruct in all of our experiments throughout the paper.",
